Invocation Name: egg stand
des: At Andrews Family Farm, we've built a high tech egg stand that counts up the number of egg cartons and makes it available to the internet. This Alexa skill allows you to find out the current count by simply asking Alexa.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
